# {{projectName}}

A DartAPI server.

## Run

```bash
dartapi run
dartapi run --port=8080
dartapi run --env=staging --watch
```

## Endpoints

| Method | Path     | Description              |
|--------|----------|--------------------------|
| GET    | /health  | Health check             |
| GET    | /hello   | Greeting from the server |

## Add features

Regenerate with additional features using the CLI:

```bash
# Auth (JWT)
dartapi create {{projectName}} --with=auth

# Database (PostgreSQL CRUD)
dartapi create {{projectName}} --with=db

# Both
dartapi create {{projectName}} --with=auth,db

# Everything (auth, db, files, websockets, metrics)
dartapi create {{projectName}} --full
```

Or generate individual components:

```bash
dartapi generate controller MyThing
dartapi generate resource Product
dartapi generate migration add_orders_table
```

## Project structure

```
bin/
  main.dart              Entry point
lib/src/
  config/
    app_config.dart      Typed environment config
    env_loader.dart      .env file loader
  controllers/
    hello_controller.dart  Example GET /hello
  core/
    dartapi.dart           DartAPI re-export
env/
  .env.dev               Development environment variables
  .env.example           Template (committed)
```
